I'd come help out Gramps.

03:02.549 --> 03:05.484
I can't believe you're even standing here.
Why is that?

03:05.552 --> 03:07.619
Well, I thought you'd be
in Berlin by now.

03:07.687 --> 03:11.323
Wasn't that what you planned to do, go see
where your mom was born and all that?

03:11.424 --> 03:14.159
Dusseldorf. Yeah.
I am gonna go soon.

03:14.227 --> 03:15.994
I have my whole... trip planned
out, actually. I just...

03:16.095 --> 03:18.039
- Yeah?
- Yeah.

03:18.064 --> 03:21.333
Here ya are, my dear.
(panting)

03:24.337 --> 03:27.072
You tell your dad to drop in
when he gets the chance, huh?

03:27.140 --> 03:30.776
I will. Thank you. I'll, um...

03:30.843 --> 03:33.912
