to be out of town.

07:11.397 --> 07:13.341
- Did you ask him about it?
- I did.

07:13.366 --> 07:15.400
He just denies it
and then he... acts like

07:15.468 --> 07:18.203
I'm being overly sus...
Hey, honey, do we have any

07:18.271 --> 07:20.138
