Private

07:20.239 --> 07:24.009
conversation.
I'll ask the caterer.

07:24.110 --> 07:26.344
K, we'll continue
the conversation later.

07:26.446 --> 07:29.915
For now just play the happy wife, OK?

07:30.016 --> 07:32.617
Ang, I'm a vet, not a politician.

07:32.718 --> 07:35.153
And I'm a divorce
attorney. Trust me.

08:16.629 --> 08:18.730
Would you excuse us for a moment?

08:21.434 --> 08:24.035
I've, uh... I've got
something for you.

08:27.940 --> 08:32.110
Happy tenth anniversary.

08:32.211 --> 08:35.280
Jeff, I don't wanna do this here.

08:35.347 --> 08:37.292
Well, what's going on?

08:39.352 --> 08:41.486
Let's just do it at home.

08:46.058 --> 08:48.527
(sizzling sound)

09:00.640 --> 09:04.009
<i>Jeff, I'm gonna ask you this
one more time.</i>

09:04.076 --> 09:06.711
And I need an honest answer.
Just don't ask me

09:06.779 --> 09:08.647
again if I'm having an affair, please.

09:08.714 --> 09:11.249
- Are you?
- No!

09:12.985 --> 09:14.929
I am

09:14.954 --> 09:17.188
so sick of you lying.

09:17.256 --> 09:19.925
(sighing)

09:37.276 --> 09:39.711
(cell phone ringing)

09:44.850 --> 09:47.719
- Hey.
- Sorry I took so long to call.

09:47.820 --> 09:51.122
How are you?
[Um... I'm OK.]

09:51.190 --> 09:53.558
Hey, when can I see you again?

09:53.659 --> 09:56.027
I miss you.
[I miss you too.]

09:56.095 --> 09:59.397
How 'bout I get us a room
tomorrow night?

09:59.498 --> 10:01.967
The Randal Garden Inn downtown?

10:02.068 --> 10:05.537
We can... order room service,

10:05.605 --> 10:07.572
[snuggle up with a movie.]

10:07.640 --> 10:10.141
OK. What time?

10:10.209 --> 10:13.645
I won't get there till after five, but
you can check in as early as three.

10:13.713 --> 10:15.580
You know, after you get off
work if you want to.

10:15.681 --> 10:18.984
[OK. Sounds good.]

10:19.085 --> 10:21.453
- Love you.
- I love you too.

10:21.554 --> 10:23.688
Bye.

10:29.295 --> 10:31.396
(exhaling)

10:34.333 --> 10:36.901
(loud music)

10:42.808 --> 10:46.478
Cheers.

10:46.579 --> 10:48.523
You know, I see that bitch sometimes.

10:48.547 --> 10:51.182
The one that turned him in.
Doesn't she go to school

10:51.283 --> 10:53.351
with you?

10:53.452 --> 10:55.812
That ho-bag dropped out a few
months after his sentencing.

10:55.836 --> 10:58.690
You can thank me for that.
I did what I could

10:58.758 --> 11:01.359
to make her life hell. What?

11:01.427 --> 11:04.229
She deserved it for lying her
ass off about my brother.

11:04.330 --> 11:06.331
Greg just told me to keep tabs

11:06.432 --> 11:08.500
on her. Find out

11:08.567 --> 11:12.203
what she's doing, where she's
going. That kind of stuff.

11:12.271 --> 11:14.973
He told me not to touch her.

11:15.041 --> 11:18.209
Speaking of touching...
Let's go to your room.

11:23.149 --> 11:26.818
(coughing)

11:26.919 --> 11:29.988
(flushing)

11:30.089 --> 11:32.033
- Too much to drink?
- I don't know.

11:32.058 --> 11:35.960
