Said I could go with him.

12:01.787 --> 12:04.656
- On the crab boat?
- It's a lot of money.

12:04.757 --> 12:07.559
How long?

12:07.660 --> 12:11.196
Couple of weeks.
Till the season's over.

12:11.297 --> 12:13.131
I leave in a few hours.

12:13.199 --> 12:16.067
It's so dangerous.

12:16.135 --> 12:18.837
Nah. Not if you know
what you're doing.

12:18.904 --> 12:20.972
Sure. I guess.

12:21.073 --> 12:23.942
Is everything OK?

12:25.979 --> 12:27.923
Greg Foster's getting out of prison.

12:27.947 --> 12:31.049
Mikey told me last night.

12:31.117 --> 12:33.585
Two years, it's all he's gonna serve.

12:33.686 --> 12:35.553
How's Mikey taking it?

12:35.654 --> 12:38.389
You know how he is.

12:38.491 --> 12:40.592
Rob a guy, beat him half
to death, you get a slap

12:40.619 --> 12:44.099
on the wrist. I got friends doing a hell of a
lot more time. For what, sticking a needle

12:44.123 --> 12:46.658
in their arms?
Be safe out there, OK?

12:48.868 --> 12:51.269
I've seen those shows
where... people get

12:51.337 --> 12:53.905
their hands caught in fishing
cables and stuff so...

12:53.973 --> 12:55.917
I will keep my hands away
from any such cables.

12:56.008 --> 12:59.110
I promise.

12:59.211 --> 13:01.846
<i>So you've been...</i>

13:01.947 --> 13:03.648
<i>throwing up off and on
for a month, but...</i>

13:03.716 --> 13:06.684
last night was the first time
you fainted?

13:06.786 --> 13:09.587
Yeah, pretty much. I have
to stop drinking tequila.

13:09.688 --> 13:11.632
It's weird though; I didn't
even feel drunk.

13:13.626 --> 13:17.662
OK, I hate to ask the obvious, but...
have you taken a pregnancy test?

13:20.733 --> 13:24.269
I can't stop thinking about her.

13:24.370 --> 13:27.272
You know. Who is she?

13:27.339 --> 13:29.574
Who is this woman...

13:29.675 --> 13:32.343
my husband's in love with?

13:32.411 --> 13:35.380
OK. What are you gonna do?

13:35.481 --> 13:38.950
Well, he said he was going out
of town tonight but, um...

13:39.051 --> 13:42.887
They're actually meeting at a hotel.

13:42.988 --> 13:45.757
I'm gonna go.
Oh... Sonia, don't.

13:45.858 --> 13:48.326
I just... I need to see

13:48.427 --> 13:52.063
what she looks like. That's it.

13:57.303 --> 14:01.072
This is...

14:01.140 --> 14:04.909
This is gonna be OK.

14:04.977 --> 14:06.937
I'm gonna see Jeff tonight
and I'm gonna tell him.

14:06.961 --> 14:09.581
Is this someone you've been
seeing for a while?

14:09.682 --> 14:12.016
Three and a half months.

14:12.117 --> 14:14.752
But he's got... a really

14:14.854 --> 14:17.789
steady job and he's
really solid. And...

14:17.890 --> 14:19.757
I know he wants kids. I mean,
he and his wife tried

14:19.825 --> 14:22.126
to have one a while ago,
but... she miscarried and

14:22.194 --> 14:25.263
he was really upset about it.
His wife? Ex-wife.

14:25.364 --> 14:28.533
I meant... ex-wife.
Chelsea.

14:28.601 --> 14:31.202
Be honest. Is...
this guy married?

14:31.270 --> 14:34.138
It's really just a matter

14:34.206 --> 14:36.166
of paperwork. I mean,
they both... want a divorce.

14:36.208 --> 14:38.243
How old is he?

14:38.310 --> 14:41.512
I love him.

14:43.749 --> 14:45.917
That's all that matters.
Everybody always gets

14:45.985 --> 14:48.786
so caught up about things like
age and money, but... none

14:48.854 --> 14:52.357
of that stuff matters. Love is
the most important thing.

14:57.429 --> 15:00.298
- What does that mean?
- <i>Liebe uberwindet</i>

15:00.399 --> 15:04.402
<i>alles.</i> "Love conquers all."
It was

15:04.503 --> 15:07.171
my mother's favorite saying.
Hey, Liz?

15:07.239 --> 15:10.441
I'll be right there.
You take your time.

15:10.509 --> 15:12.477
I'll take care of these people.
Thanks.

15:51.617 --> 15:53.561
My boyfriend made
a reservation for tonight.

15:53.585 --> 15:56.287
- What's the name?
- Chelsea Sheridans, but he said

15:56.355 --> 15:58.556
it might be under his name.

