Oh, yeah, no. I... I'm not
officially here.

17:43.228 --> 17:46.130
I just came to take care of some
stuff, paperwork. Oh, hey, how was

17:46.231 --> 17:49.200
the anniversary party?
Uh... It was good, thanks.

18:01.013 --> 18:03.481
God, Jeff...

18:14.927 --> 18:18.029
- Hey.
- Hey.

18:30.342 --> 18:33.511
I'm happy to see you.
Me too.

18:33.579 --> 18:35.523
Been counting the minutes all day.

18:46.458 --> 18:48.426
